title: [PORN Advertisements] Shai Wear 2006 Summer Catalogue Videos
description:
2006 Summer clothing catalogue for Shai Wear clothing, Paris. These videos were used with an interactive application that would allow you to mouse-over dots that would appear on the screen next to an item being advertised and view more details about it.

Video by agence7seven [http://www.agence7seven.com/]
Audio by nventa [http://www.nventa.net/]
